# Pin text files to LF. The kit reads these and pipes their contents into
# CLAUDE.md / AGENTS.md / .claude/skills/*. If CRLF leaks in (Windows checkouts
# with core.autocrlf=true), it surfaces inside the Docker test image as
# `$'\r': command not found` for scripts, and breaks `grep '^…$'` anchors in
# tests that scan the rendered CLAUDE.md. Belt-and-suspenders: the Docker test
# image also runs a CRLF strip during build (test/Dockerfile.test).

*.sh text eol=lf
*.bash text eol=lf
*.md text eol=lf
*.yaml text eol=lf
*.yml text eol=lf
*.mjs text eol=lf
*.js text eol=lf
*.json text eol=lf

bin/agent-kit text eol=lf
bootstrap.sh text eol=lf
